=== EMERGENCY_BROADCAST ===
# id: 97
# title: The Emergency Broadcast
# chinese_title: 紧急广播
# category: Terminal
# mode: dungeon

An emergency broadcast system loops a station-wide message in multiple languages. The Chinese version contains subtle differences from the other translations — extra characters that form a hidden message. Someone embedded a secret in the broadcast decades ago.

* [Decode the hidden message in the Chinese text]
  ~ gain_radical("言")
  "秘" (mì) — secret, hidden. The radical "言" relates to language.
* [Compare all language versions systematically]
  ~ gain_xp(25)
  "比" (bǐ) — to compare
* [Shut down the broadcast to conserve power]
  ~ gain_gold(10)
  "停" (tíng) — to stop, to halt
* [Re-record the broadcast with updated info]
  ~ gain_xp(15)
  "播" (bō) — to broadcast, to spread
